       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CUSTOMER-INFO.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 CUSTOMER-ID               PIC X(9).
       01 ACCOUNT-BALANCE           PIC 9(5)V99.
       01 ACCOUNT-BALANCE-EDITED    PIC 0ZZZZ.99.
       01 INTEREST-RATE             PIC 9V99.
       01 INTEREST-RATE-EDITED      PIC 9.99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       BEGIN.
           MOVE "CUST00123" TO CUSTOMER-ID.
           MOVE 1234.56 TO ACCOUNT-BALANCE.
           MOVE ACCOUNT-BALANCE TO ACCOUNT-BALANCE-EDITED.
           MOVE 5.75 TO INTEREST-RATE.
           MOVE INTEREST-RATE TO INTEREST-RATE-EDITED.

           DISPLAY "Customer ID     : " CUSTOMER-ID.
           DISPLAY "Account Balance : " ACCOUNT-BALANCE-EDITED.
           DISPLAY "Interest Rate   : " INTEREST-RATE-EDITED "%".

           STOP RUN.
